  "decision_conditions": [
    "By virtue of the existing ridgeline and resultant flat roof, the proposed development is not a hip to gable roof enlargement. As the eaves of the roof of the original dwellinghouse would not be maintained or reinstated as a result, the proposal fails to comply with Schedule 2, Part 1, Class B, paragraph B.2(b)(i)(aa) of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended).",
    "The cubic content of the resulting roof space would exceed the cubic content of the original roof space by more than 50 cubic metres. As such, the proposed development is contrary to Schedule 2, Part 1, Class B, paragraph B.1(d) of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended)."
